T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"e24d18c5-67c0-4998-ad73-6becff8c2f17","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"おそらくMutagenで改善するんじゃないかなぁ","ts":"1581909683.018300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ze5Db"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"aec797e9-6d2c-47fb-aead-3ae1f0d8d59e","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"rsyncでホストと手動で同期するのが、当時はいちばんバランスが良かった。","ts":"1581909834.019100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"tvneh"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"C4FB639C-B946-494B-9C11-4C3BAEF0C870","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"ですよね、自分も最初それでやってました","ts":"1581909890.019600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"FU1"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"e896b79a-d16b-43e6-9b61-3fba93c3636c","type":"message","user":"UNJ2DANJC","text":"rails×reactの事情はよくわからないので差し出がましいかもしれませんが、そもそも開発用ビルドを無理にdockerでやる必要があるのか気になります。nodeもrailsもmacのネイティブで動かせるのでは？","ts":"1581910706.023300","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"+1","count":2,"users":["UNCH7K9ND","UAVDYVA82"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"3Dfa7"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"0720FC59-71AA-4C27-BB9B-52875537343B","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"最近は割とDockerに寄せてることが多い印象です\n（自社だけじゃなく他社でも）\n構築が簡単なのと本番と同じイメージをベースにしたものを使えるのがでかい","ts":"1581910860.025200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"tm3=j"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"892b71b1-0c52-4d88-933a-ea22ee4ca7a5","type":"message","user":"UNJ2DANJC","text":"本番と同じという観点でいうとwebpackがproductionとdevelopで分かれているとdocker以前にそもそも全く別物なのではと思ったり...\n自分のところもreact使ってますけどフロントエンド開発者はバックエンドのみビルド済のdockerでフロントエンドのreactはネイティブでやっています。\nlinuxでもmacでもwindowsでもnodeさえ入っていればyarn install とyarn startで開発できています。\nもしかしてwebpackでビルドしたあとのファイルを更にrailsでバンドルするみたいな構成だとしたらやっぱdockerが楽なのかな....","ts":"1581911684.033600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"dUn"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"f29487ec-5266-41cc-8f64-805383b772f6","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"Nodeについてはほぼネイティブでできると思っています\nRubyなどについてはRubyバージョンの固定やOSで微妙に動作が異なるなどがあると思っていて、実際にあったのはAlpineのバグで浅めでSystemStackErrorが発生する問題に気付けるなどありました\n\nあとはミドルウェアとの連携などで、DBやRedisをホストマシンに依存刺せないとか、Seleniumが必要な場合に一通で環境が通るようにするとかなんだかんだ色々メリットはあると思います","ts":"1581913866.036500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"5xg"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"2a1a75a6-d44c-4344-b50c-eb56c0dbad2e","type":"message","user":"U8CC7MDCL","text":"selenium…ChromeDriver…chrome自動更新…ウッ頭が…","ts":"1581915318.037700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"c+uf8"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"}]
